e those well-known cliffs...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/36.mp3","time_start":103.14,"time_end":105.25},{"position":37,"content":"I've forgotten the name of them...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/37.mp3","time_start":105.45,"time_end":106.97},{"position":38,"content":"Oh don't worry - I can look them up.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/38.mp3","time_start":106.97,"time_end":109.83},{"position":39,"content":"I've also been surfing in County Mayo,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/39.mp3","time_start":110.04,"time_end":112.89},{"position":40,"content":"which is less well-known for surfing, but we had a really good time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/40.mp3","time_start":112.99,"time_end":117.2},{"position":41,"content":"That was a few years ago when the kids were younger.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/41.mp3","time_start":117.67,"time_end":120.37},{"position":42,"content":"There's a good surf school at Carrowniskey beach.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/42.mp3","time_start":120.69,"time_end":124.12},{"position":43,"content":"How do you spell that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/43.mp3","time_start":124.29,"time_end":125.84},{"position":44,"content":"Carrowniskey","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-2