 actually, it tends to rain more in August than in the spring or autumn.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/62.mp3","time_start":183.92,"time_end":188.95},{"position":63,"content":"September's my favourite month because the water is warmer then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/63.mp3","time_start":189.11,"time_end":193.38},{"position":64,"content":"The only problem is that the kids are back to school then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/64.mp3","time_start":193.55,"time_end":197.24},{"position":65,"content":"I know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/65.mp3","time_start":197.3,"time_end":198.16},{"position":66,"content":"But one good thing about Irish summers is that it doesn't get too hot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/66.mp3","time_start":198.4,"time_end":203.05},{"position":67,"content":"The average temperature is about 19 degrees","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/67.mp3","time_start":203.29,"time_end":207.01},{"position":68,"content":"and it usually doesn't go above 25 degrees.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/68.mp3","time_start":207.15,"time_end":210.74},{"position":69,"content":"That sounds alright.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/69.mp3","time_start":210.85,"time_end":212.41},{"position":70,"content":"Now what about costs?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/70.mp3","time_start":212.64,"time_end":214.78},{"position":71,"content":"Surfing is a pretty cheap holiday really,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/71.mp3","time_start":214.87,"time_end":217.55},{"position":72,"content":"the only cost is the hire of equipment.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/72.mp3","time_start":217.79,"time_end":220.54},{"position":73,"content":"You can expect to pay a daily rate of about 30 euros for the hire of a wetsuit and board,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/73.mp3","time_start":220.73,"time_end":227.41},{"position":74,"content":"but you can save about 40 euros if you hire by the week.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/74.mp3","time_start":227.94,"time_end":232.05},{"position":75,"content":"That's not too bad.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/75.mp3","time_start":232.14,"time_end":233.61},{"position":76,"content":"No.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/76.mp3","time_start":233.61,"time_end":234.15},{"position":77,"content":"It's important to make sure you get good quality wetsuits.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/77.mp3","time_start":234.63,"time_end":238.29},{"position":78,"content":"You'll all get too cold if you don't.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/78.mp3","time_start":238.49,"time_end":240.78},{"position":79,"content":"And make sure you also get boots.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/79.mp3","time_start":240.94,"time_end":243.88},{"position":80,"content":"They keep your feet warm and it's easier to surf with them on too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/80.mp3","time_start":244.15,"time_end":248.6},{"position":81,"content":"OK. Well, thanks very much...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-3-section-1-2022-12-24-21-56-42/81.mp3","time_start":248.73,"time_end":251.66}]}